{"content": "<h2>The Artist: apocalypse</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>World building is often thrown around in cryptoart yet few have the patience to bring it to life over the multiple years it takes. Apocalypse is the exception. <a href=\"https://apocalypse.art/screenplay/\">Read the 'On The Run' screenplay</a> for the 2025 short film...that is the crescendo for a release of characters over the last three years 2021-2024.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"725\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi-1024x991.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi-1024x991.jpeg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi-300x290.jpeg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi-768x743.jpeg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi-600x580.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/GgJqhyIbYAIyBWi.jpeg 1070w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: InFlux</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>InFlux is Apocalypse Studio's magnum opus, with 333 handmade unique artworks told across three chapters. The first chapter 'The Origins' (some shown below) consisted of 30 artworks, has 22 collectoors and sold for a total of $16.3k in October 2023.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm80 248c0 44.112-35.888 80-80 80s-80-35.888-80-80 35.888-80 80-80 80 35.888 80 80z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tChapter One | The Origins\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm80 248c0 44.112-35.888 80-80 80s-80-35.888-80-80 35.888-80 80-80 80 35.888 80 80z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tChapter Two | The Ordeal\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm80 248c0 44.112-35.888 80-80 80s-80-35.888-80-80 35.888-80 80-80 80 35.888 80 80z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tChapter Three | The Oversoul (unreleased)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\thttps://videos.files.wordpress.com/BiX4ed99/screen-recording-2025-01-09-at-11.08.29e280afam.mov\t\t\n\t\t<p>The Ordeal is Chapter Two of Influx and was released a year later in October 2024. The Ordeal collection consists of 133 1/1s that inhabit a range of worlds including Chaos (29), Mass Destruction (29), Anarchy (28), Social Sculpture (19), Underworld (11), Creators (10) and Heavens (7).</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Berserker</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Berserker lives in the world of Mass Destruction. The medalled military officer throws his hands up as if to announce or exclaim something and yet is simultaneously eviscerated into a thousand shards of claret. A contrast to the levelled grey cities that sullen the background.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/berserker.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/berserker.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/berserker-300x200.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/berserker-768x512.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/berserker-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Berserker by Apocalypse collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>On The Line</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The Meeings is one of Apocalypse's earliest minted work, pre-dating The Influx. The Meeings are available to view in the Hall of Meeings on The Line.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"The Meeings apocalyptic visions — some beautiful, some terrible. They have all manner of intentions. There are 49 Meeings, all 1/1s.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Apocalypse</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/apocalypse/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"469\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-1024x641.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-1024x641.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-300x188.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-768x481.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-1536x962.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-2048x1282.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-1320x826.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-09-at-11.28.28 AM-600x376.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>The Hall of Meeings on The Line 77 by Apocalypse</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/apocalypse/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tApocalypse | Line 77\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}